official_title: To provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain frozen concentrated orange juice entries to correct an error that was made in connection with the original liquidation.

summary.text: Directs the U.S. Customs Service to liquidate or reliquidate (refund the duties on) certain entries of frozen concentrated orange juice.

titles.title: To provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain frozen concentrated orange juice entries to correct an error that was made in connection with the original liquidation.
